WEBVTT

00:00:30.520 --> 00:00:32.000
What a wonderful idea, right?

00:00:32.880 --> 00:00:34.096
What could go wrong?

00:00:34.120 --> 00:00:35.640
(Laughter)

00:00:36.400 --> 00:00:38.456
Well, there were 40 of us to start with,

00:00:38.480 --> 00:00:40.936
and every time I heard
someone's name called,

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:42.760
I would give out the heartiest cheer.

00:00:43.280 --> 00:00:45.776
And then there were 20 people left,

00:00:45.800 --> 00:00:47.576
and 10 people left,

00:00:47.600 --> 00:00:48.960
and five left ...

00:00:49.560 --> 00:00:50.936
and three left.

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:52.160
And I was one of them.

00:00:52.720 --> 00:00:54.320
And the compliments stopped.

00:00:55.560 --> 00:00:57.600
Well, at that moment, I was crying.

00:00:58.600 --> 00:01:00.616
And the teacher was freaking out.